            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "If I remember correctly...the flower that waits for rain should be around here somewhere..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Since it's so close to the workshop, I wouldn't be surprised if I've seen it before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I better refresh my memory..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, let's see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "\"During the rainy season, the valley becomes a roaring river.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "\"The pretty, pink petals give off a fragrance similar to a well-leavened wine.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...I've never seen it rain so hard that it turned a valley into a river..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Up to this point, I've seen traces of erosion all around. Could it have been caused by water flowing through here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "If the flower only blooms when it's raining, then it must need water..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Maybe it's just a seed or bulb that's waiting for it to rain..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "If that's the case, then the flower has to still be in the valley somewhere."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I know! If it has to do with plants... Pana! Can you find it!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x205,
            "name_id": 0x1f,
            "extra_id": 0x216,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oink moo!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x205,
            "name_id": 0x1f,
            "extra_id": 0x21c,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Oink! *munch* *munch*<CR>...Moo!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yeah...I shoulda known it wasn't gonna be that easy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I need to come up with a way..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...hmm...I can't think of anything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Maybe I need to study synthesis some more..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I know! I think there was a tool that would be helpful in a book I read before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Okay! I should head back and retool my strategy."
